title: Unnatural Objects
description: Tal Kisbee travels to Hong Kong on a whim. He accidentally infiltrates a group of crazy ex-pats and finds himself propelled into a world of crooks, scamsters and smugglers. As he sinks deeper into the Hong Kong underworld, he gets involved with increasingly serious crime. But all his dangerous or violent actions seem to be connected by a common factor: His sinister new friend Racknell.Available for Kindle now.Please take a look at the trailer: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GCJIum...Please download it here: http://www.amazon.co.uk/Unnatural-Obj...
author: Paul Monaghan
